com.upsight.android

Class UpsightContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • com.upsight.android.UpsightContext

  • public class UpsightContext
extends android.content.ContextWrapper
    The UpsightContext used to execute all Upsight APIs. This is a wrapper around your base Context, providing extra functionality made available by the Upsight SDK.

                      UpsightDataStore dataStore,
                      UpsightLogger logger)
        The UpsightContext used to execute all Upsight APIs. This is a wrapper around your base Context, providing extra functionality made available by the Upsight SDK.
        Parameters:
        baseContext - The base Context.
        sdkPlugin - The identifier of the SDK plugin used; or null if no plugin is used.
        appToken - The application token specified in the Manifest.
        publicKey - The public key specified in the Manifest.
        sid - The SID, a unique identifier generated for this installation.
        dataStore - The UpsightDataStore.
        logger - The UpsightLogger.
